data.description: H12059Escape to your private oasis in this stunning 2-story, fully concrete home in Golden Gate Estates. With 4+Den, 4 baths, and over 2 acres, it offers seclusion and luxury. Features include a 2-car attached garage, a detached 3-car garage with AC, and an AC-equipped 1-car detached garage for your toys. Poured concrete with 2 vinyl tents adds to the appeal. The saltwater pool and spa, with a waterfall from the built-in gazebo/spa, are surrounded by a colossal 2-story screened lanai—a scene from a storybook. The primary bedroom is a retreat with French door access to decking leading to the spa and ground floor. Inside, find wood flooring, dual vanity, shower heads, a soaking tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. An en suite on the 2nd floor adds convenience. Remaining bedrooms are generously sized, featuring a jack/jill bathroom access. Entertaining is a breeze with a 2-story vaulted great room, a kitchen with ample space, a 5-burner GAS range, a walk-in pantry, a formal dining area, and a versatile den/home office. Enjoy peace of mind with a 2018 roof, in-residence laundry, a chute from the 2nd floor, and a welcoming French door entry.Privacy takes center stage in this special home
